stimulus: Welcome to the experiment. Press any key to begin.

In each round, you will see three headlines.

Please click on the headline you would most like to read, and you will get an opportunity to read the articles you select later in the experiment.

There will be six rounds of articles to view. This should take approximately two minutes.

Press any key to begin.
